---
import Layout from "../layouts/layouts.astro";
---

<Layout title="Leaving Checklist | Nardelli" currentPath={Astro.url.pathname}>
	<h1>👋 A Presto <span class="h1Sub">(see you soon)</span></h1>

<section class="heroCard">
	<div class="leaveGrid">
		<div>
			<p>
				We hope you’ve had a wonderful time in Nardelli. Rather than saying “ciao”, we say “a presto”
				(<em>see you soon</em>) when leaving. Like us, you may have fallen in love with what Umbria &amp; Tuscany
				has to offer and might return again sometime. Safe travels, and we hope to welcome you back again.
			</p>

			<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
				A few quick steps before you go helps keep the house ready for the next family member or friend to enjoy:
			</p>

            <h2>Leaving Checklist</h2>

			<ul class="leaveList">
				<li>
					Wash &amp; dry sheets (<a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/jUqQzZuZnMzdcGYz7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">24 Hour Self Service Laundry - Bring Cash</a>)
				</li>
				<li>Fold cleaned and dried sheets and leave them on the bed(s) for the next visitor</li>
                <li>
					Clear / clean fridge &amp; cupboards of any perishable goods (it could be a long time until the next guest visits)
				</li>
				<li>Remove any bins or items for recycling</li>
				<li>Turn off boiler switch in kitchen</li>
				<li>Turn off water mains outside</li>
				<li>Turn off gas mains outside</li>
				<li>Close windows / shutters / door into the garden</li>
				<li>Turn off all lights</li>
				<li>Turn off the electricity (flip fuse switch down)</li>
				<li>Lock front door (and garden gate if open)</li>
				<li>Return keys to lockbox</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<img
			src="/photos/Ciao.jpeg"
			alt="A presto"
			loading="lazy"
		/>
	</div>
</section>

	<style>
        .heroCard {
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 12px 0 18px;
        }

        .leaveGrid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .leaveGrid img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            min-height: 360px; /* helps it span the message + list nicely */
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
            border-radius: calc(var(--radius) - 2px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .leaveList {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .leaveList li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        @media (min-width: 860px) {
            .leaveGrid {
                grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 0.75fr;
                align-items: stretch; /* makes the image column stretch vertically */
            }
        }

.h1Sub {
	color: var(--muted);
	font-style: italic;
	font-weight: 600;
}

    </style>
</Layout>
​

